      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study was completed; however GCI for hemolysis index on the finest mesh is 15.3%, exceeding the MRL 5 threshold of 5%. Asymptotic convergence range is not achieved (observed order p=1.1 vs. formal order p=2). Achieved level 2 reflects that a study was performed but convergence criteria are unmet."
