      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/output-comparison-mrl5",
      "rationale": "Mean absolute error of 38% between CFD-predicted and measured hemolysis index across 5 operating points. Systematic under-prediction at high shear rates (>500 s⁻¹) suggests model form inadequacy. No statistical equivalence test or validation metric threshold was pre-specified; post-hoc comparison does not satisfy MRL 5 requirements. Achieved level 2 reflects quantitative comparison performed but acceptance threshold not met."
