      "rationale": "The hemolysis index (HI) is directly the clinical quantity of interest and is computed as the primary model output. However, secondary QOIs including platelet activation index and thrombus formation risk are not modeled, and their exclusion is not formally justified against the COU scope. Achieved level 3 reflects that the primary QOI is correctly identified and computed but secondary QOI coverage is incomplete for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
