      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic pump geometry rather than the actual device geometry, and operating conditions span only 3 of the 5 required flow-speed combinations. The validation domain does not include the extreme low-flow high-speed condition most clinically relevant to VAD patients. Achieved level 2 reflects partial geometric and operational relevance with significant domain gaps."
    },
